    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 18 or older.

          -  Healthy, euvolemic volunteers and critically ill patients who are already in an
             intensive care unit and who will have a central venous catheter placed as part of
             their planned medical treatment.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Inability to use ultrasound to measure jugular vein (neck brace or bandage), &quot;code&quot;
             situation.
      </textblock>
